   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" mid="7" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> What happened there? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" mid="8" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> Where is that place? </htmlL]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" mid="9" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> What did Queen Narsilla requested? </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_answer link_index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" mid="10" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html> I'm sorry to hear that </html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="6"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>Another adventure? Do you want me to tell you what I've gone through because of damn Queen Narsilla? She asked us to go to the place where humans hasn't been for a long time and I experienced my worst nightmare there. </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-a" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>What happened? I don't recall it all but I saw was the white aurora that was about to burn my brain. That white aurora was the aurora of destruction. <FONT color=#7e12d2> (Loffy shakes as if he is in fear) </FONT> Goddess!! Please forgive us!!! </html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>
It was the closest place to hell on this continent. I remember now.. Ah, my head is killing me. Go away! Leave me alone. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Loffy covers his head and suffer from it. I don't think I can talk about it more.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar $<BR>
Request? It was to find a route. Just find a route. That was a lie. That was a road to hell. Ah, I got a headache. I have rest now. <FONT color=#7e12d2>(Loffy doesn't want to talk about it anymore.)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n087_beggar-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Loffy the Beggar$<BR>Trying to be nice again? You better leave this trash town. Haha, if you stay too close to trash you will become one. </html>]]></talk_question>
